sbol:Collection.dcterms:title: iGEM Parts Registry
sbol:Collection.dcterms:description: The iGEM Registry is a growing collection of genetic parts that can be mixed and matched to build synthetic biology devices and systems. As part of the synthetic biology community's efforts to make biology easier to engineer, it provides a source of genetic parts to iGEM teams and academic labs.

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K1222001
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: pGFP (T7 promoter+lac operator+GFP antisense"3"+T7 terminator+Lac promoter+LacI)
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: This part is IPTG inducible for regulating the production of GFP antisense.We have designed four sets of GFP antisense to inhibit GFP.(BBa_K1222987, BBa_K1222986, BBa_K1222985)but we have only shown one(GFP antisense 3) of the four antisense as the other three are relatively similar just the GFP antisense is different. The GFP designed is used to test its efficiency on inhibiting(knockdown) the target genes.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Tingling Ke
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: This part is composed of previous igem biobrick got form igem foundation(BBa_I719005, BBa_K731721, BBa_I14032, BBa_C0012)and parts we constructed(BBa_K1222987, BBa_K1222986, BBa_K1222985).

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K1222003
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Transcription of the Lac promoter is regulated by Lacl, (type of repressor protein) and then combines with the Lac operator sequence thereby inhibiting the transcription process.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Tingling Ke

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: P(Lac) IQ
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Vikram Vijayan, Allen Hsu, Lawrence Fomundam

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K731721
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: This is a short terminator by T7phage that we tested with our new teminators' characterization system.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Giacomo Giacomelli, Anna Depetris
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: We amplified it directly from pET21b.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: This is a standard sequence, very used in many constructs. As i don't have any design considerations i can say that generally to make screening gels of such short segments is preferable to use TBE1X instead of TAE1X.

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K1222985
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: A short sequence that inhibits GFP gene is regulated by lac operator .
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Yu-Chun Huang
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: We designed and made it by artificial synthesis.
